          {
            "id": "3",
            "title": "Fall of Civilizations",
            "slug": "fall-of-civilizations",
            "html": "<p>I fall asleep to an episode every night at 75% speed. It’s absolutely worth $3 per month to support Paul’s brilliant work and nix the YouTube fuckery. Start with Carthage, but be forewarned: it’s a heartbreak.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6dbdVhVSat8&list=PLR7yrLMHm11X6-M_usCj5H-gdstyWNLXQ&index=21\">Visit &rarr;</a></p>",
