          {
            "id": "6",
            "title": "Midwife",
            "slug": "midwife",
            "html": "<p>Madeline Johnston’s voice sounds like it’s fighting its way through the static on a radio in the kitchen of a different decade. This is beautiful vapor, the afterimage of a flashbulb popping off after the encore of a band that littered the stage with only the finest reverb pedals.</p><p><a href=\"https://heavenmetal.bandcamp.com/?ref=jamesreeves.co\">Visit &rarr;</a></p>",
